This project is an experimetal renderer for me to use. 
Before "make" the renderer, you need to install glm library. 
Current implementation is verified on Ubuntu 14.04.
(In Ubuntu, you can just "sudo apt-get install libglm-dev".)

Features include

* Thin lens (Not fully verified yet)
* Path tracing with next event estimation
* Supported material: Lambertian, Glossy, Glass

Guide

* Before make the project, create a new "obj" folder, make clean, then make